  "title": "Civil & Structural Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Undertake design development and detailed designs</li>\n  <li>Attend site/project meetings with clients, consultants and contractor</li>\n  <li>Familiar with engineering software and the latest code of practice</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications/Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A good degree in Civil / Structural Engineering from a recognized University.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years and above of working experience in a Civil &amp; Structural consultancy firm. (An engineer with six years and above of working experience will be considered for a senior position.)</li>\n  <li>Possess good communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently or/and in a team.</li>\n</ul>",
