    "description": "<p><strong>WRX Engineers Pte Ltd </strong>is a Civil & Structural Consultant Company handles projects from a wide spectrum of customers in Singapore, be they in the government agencies, industrial, commercial or residential markets. Our company is involved with the designing of various structures and their maintenance as well; giving advice to customers should changes be required so as to maintain ongoing relationships with them. We are a solution provider as we solve various problems using our knowledge and expertise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>WRX Engineers Pte Ltd </strong>encourages individual ability and creativity in our team. Team members are also given opportunities to gain more experience and confidence through consolidating requirements from customers and coordinating with other disciplines, specialist consultants and contractors. As a growing company, we also promote continuous self-improvement by encouraging team members to take upgrading courses.</p>\r\n",
